## Simple Habits to Improve Focus and Concentration

Here''s how you can rebuild your attention with practical, everyday steps:

### 1. Get Moving with Light Exercise

Start smallâ€”grab some dumbbells or take a brisk walk. Regular activity boosts your energy, helping you concentrate without feeling wiped out.

