### [Schulte Table](/games/schulte-table)
Enhance your information processing speed and attention distributionâ€”key components of effective working memory performance.

### [Larger Number](/games/larger-number)
Train your brain to make quick decisions while holding information in mind, strengthening the neural pathways essential for efficient working memory.

Just 15 minutes of targeted practice daily can help expand your working memory capacity and enhance your learning efficiency! ðŸ§  ',
